e":"彩","body":"奈央小姐……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"sad01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event257-07-046","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":226}],"windowDisplayName":"奈央","body":"我也請了很多地方幫忙斡旋過了。\n結果看來他們依舊硬是登出來了呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":226,"motionName":"nnf01","expressionName":"smile03","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":226,"voiceId":"event257-07-047","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"麻彌","body":"奈央小姐，該不會\n那時候的信件就是……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"sad01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event257-07-048","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":226}],"windowDisplayName":"奈央","body":"嗯。\n在這種重要的時機讓你們感到動搖，真的很抱歉","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":226,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"sad01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":226,"voiceId":"event257-07-049","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":226}],"windowDisplayName":"奈央","body":"雖然可能會有點長……\n但可以讓我親自跟你們說明嗎？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"m